nt-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">배제 신고 방법</span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">가</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">회피</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">배제 신고 시스템 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">(nDRIMS </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">탑재</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">을 통한 개인별 해당사항 신고</span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">1) </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">접근경로 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">: nDRIMS </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">학부 </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">학부입시</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">입시관리</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">회피배제 신고</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」</span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">2) </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">입력방법 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">조회</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">행추가</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」→ </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">신청상세정보 내용 입력 </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">저장</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」→「</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">입학처 제출</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;mso-hansi-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">」 </span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;\">나</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.4pt;\">상</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;\">기 시스템 사용이 원활하지 않은 경우에만</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">, [</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;\">붙임</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">] </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;\">작성하여 그룹웨어 메일로 제출</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;font-weight:bold;\">수신인 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">: </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;font-weight:bold;\">입학실 한윤수</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.3pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">)</span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">신고 기한 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">: </span><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">2025.09.12.(</span></u><u><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">금</span></u><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">) </span></u><u><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">까지</span></u></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">6. </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">상시 회피</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">(</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">자진신고</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">) </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">안내</span><br/>\n<span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">가</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.4pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">회피</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;font-weight:bold;\">·</span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-weight:bold;\">배제 신고 시스템을 통해 상시 회피 등록이 가능함</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p class=\"0\"><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;\">나</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-0.9pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.2pt;\">우리대학 교직원 중 친족ㆍ친지가 본교 입학 전형에 지원할 경우</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:-2.2pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;\">, </span><span style=\"font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;letter-spacing:-2.2pt;\">반드시 전형 시작 전 회피 등록을 해야 함</span></p>",
    "본문": "교육부 대입 부정방지\n(\n회피\n·\n배제\n)\n지침 및 우리대학 입학전형 회피\n·\n배제 규정 제\n5\n조에 따라 수시모집에 지원한 우리대학 교직원의 자녀\n,\n친\n·\n인척\n,\n특수한 관계자 현황을 파악하고자 하오니 해당자는 다음과 같이 협조하여 주시기 바랍니다\n.\n1.\n전형 명칭\n:\n2026\n학년도\n수시모집 학생부종합전형\n/\n학생부교과전형\n/\n논술전형\n/\n실기전형\n2.\n파악 대상\n가\n.\n본인 또는 그 배우자나 배우자이었던 사람이 입학전형에 응시한 학생과\n「\n민법\n」\n제\n777\n조에 따른 친족인 경우\n※\n민법 제\n777\n조\n(\n친족의 범위\n) :\n8\n촌 이내의 혈족\n, 4\n촌 이내의 인척\n,\n배우자\n나\n.\n본인 또는 그 배우자나 배우자이었던 사람이 입학전형에 응시한 학생을 그 학생이 응\n시한 입학전형의 입학연도가\n개시되는 날부터 직전\n3\n년 이내에\n「\n학원의 설립ㆍ운영\n및 과외교습에 관한 법률\n」\n에 따라 교습하거나 과외교습한 경우\n다\n.\n본인 또는 그 배우자나 배우자이었던 사람이 입학전형에 응시\n한 학생을\n그 학생이 응\n시한 입학전형의 입학연도가 개시되는 날부터 직전\n3\n년 이내에\n「\n고등교육법\n」\n,\n「\n초\nㆍ중등교육법\n」\n및 그 밖의 법령에 따른 학교에서 교육한 경우\n라\n.\n본인 또는 그 배\n우자의\n친지\n(\n친\n·\n인척이 아니더라도 친\n·\n인척에 버금가는 친분관계에 있\n는 자의 자녀포함\n)\n3.\n수시모집 주요 일정\n구 분\n일 정\n비 고\n원서접수\n2025. 09. 10.(\n수\n) 10:00 ~ 09. 12.(\n금\n) 17:00\n인터넷 원서접수\n실기고사\n체육교육과\n2025. 09. 25.(\n목\n) ~ 09. 29.(\n월\n)\n연극학부\n-\n실기형\n(\n기초실기\n)\n2025. 09. 23.(\n화\n) ~ 09. 27.(\n토\n)\n(\n종합실기\n)\n2025. 10. 22.(\n수\n) ~ 10. 25.(\n토\n)\n연극학부\n-\n특기형\n2025. 10. 25.(\n토\n)\n예정\n스포츠문화학과\n(\n축구\n)\n2025. 10. 28.(\n화\n)\n(\n야구\n)\n2025. 10. 29.(\n수\n) ~ 10. 30.(\n목\n)\n(\n농구\n)\n2025. 10. 31.(\n금\n)\n국어국문\n·\n문예창작학부\n2025. 10. 19.(\n일\n)\n미술학부\n2025. 10. 03.(\n금\n)\n한국음악과\n2025. 10. 22.(\n수\n) ~ 10. 25.(\n토\n)\n최초합격자 발표\n(\n학생부교과전형\n,\n실기전형\n)\n2025. 11. 28.(\n금\n)\n예정\n논술고사\n2025. 11. 16.(\n일\n)\n학생부종합전형 면접고사\n2025. 12. 05.(\n금\n) ~ 12. 07.(\n일\n)\n최초합격자 발표\n(\n학생부종합전형\n,\n논술전형\n)\n2025. 12. 12.(\n금\n)\n예정\n4.\n회피\n·\n배제 신고 방법\n가\n.\n회피\n·\n배제 신고 시스템\n(nDRIMS\n탑재\n)\n을 통한 개인별 해당사항 신고\n1)\n접근경로\n: nDRIMS\n학부\n→「\n학부입시\n」→「\n입시관리\n」→「\n회피배제 신고\n」\n2)\n입력방법\n:\n「\n조회\n」→「\n행추가\n」→\n신청상세정보 내용 입력\n→「\n저장\n」→「\n입학처 제출\n」\n나\n.\n상\n기 시스템 사용이 원활하지 않은 경우에만\n, [\n붙임\n]\n작성하여 그룹웨어 메일로 제출\n(\n수신인\n:\n입학실 한윤수\n)\n5.\n신고 기한\n:\n2025.09.12.(\n금\n)\n까지\n6.\n상시 회피\n(\n자진신고\n)\n안내\n가\n.\n회피\n·\n배제 신고 시스템을 통해 상시 회피 등록이 가능함\n나\n.\n우리대학 교직원 중 친족ㆍ친지가 본교 입학 전형에 지원할 경우\n,\n반드시 전형 시작 전 회피 등록을 해야 함",
